Class SimpleQueue<E>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.github.dm.jrt.core.util.SimpleQueue<E>
  • Type Parameters:
    E - the element type.

    public class SimpleQueue<E>
extends Object
    Minimal implementation of a light-weight queue storing elements into dynamically increasing circular buffer.

    Created by davide-maestroni on 09/27/2014.
